compare_instance_obs(25.10)                        compare_instance_obs(25.10)

Name
       compare_instance_obs - Compares a layer's instance obstruction shape of
       the current design in the memory with the specified reference file

Syntax
       compare_instance_obs

       [-help]

       <ref_obs_shape_file>[-report <file_name>]

       Compares  a layer's instance obstruction shape of the current design in
       the memory with the specified reference file.

Parameters
       -help  Prints a brief description that includes the  type  and  default
              information for each compare_instance_obs parameter.

              For  a  detailed  description of the command and all its parame-
              ters, use the man command:

              man compare_instance_obs

       <ref_obs_shape_file>
              Specifies the name of the reference obstruction shape file.

       -report <record_file_name>
              Specifies the file to record difference between the  obstruction
              shapes.

Related Information
       write_instance_obs

